        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-60886d88-72c3-4136-b760-c309974a994d">
                Mr. Speaker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-60886d88-72c3-4136-b760-c309974a994d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-10-04/debates/280f43ec-c8d3-4540-a421-5bb1ea565cf2/TheKingSIllness#contribution-60886d88-72c3-4136-b760-c309974a994d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As there is a minute or two before Black Rod comes, perhaps I might be allowed to say that, not knowing that anything was going to be said in the House of Commons about the King's illness, I, without authority, I admit, wrote to the King's Private Secretary and said that I thought it would be the wish of the present House of Commons to express sympathy with the Queen in the King's illness. I have received a letter from Sir Alan Lascelles, the King's Private Secretary, saying that the Queen asks me to thank hon. Members for their sympathy and their earnest wish for the King's early and complete recovery. I thought I would report that to the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-60886d88-72c3-4136-b760-c309974a994d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-10-04/debates/280f43ec-c8d3-4540-a421-5bb1ea565cf2/TheKingSIllness#contribution-60886d88-72c3-4136-b760-c309974a994d">
